<h2>About the Game</h2>
<p>
<strong>🫧 Bubble Pop Legend – Play Free Online</strong><br><br>
🎯 About Bubble Pop Legend<br>

Bubble Pop Legend is a fun and addictive bubble shooter game where your goal is to clear the board by matching colors.
 Aim carefully, shoot bubbles, and create combinations to pop them efficiently.<br>

With simple gameplay and increasing difficulty, each level challenges your accuracy, planning, and strategy. 
The more bubbles you clear in one shot, the higher your score.<br><br>

<strong>⭐ Key Features</strong><br><br>

🎯 Color Matching Gameplay – Match 3 or more bubbles<br>
💥 Chain Reactions – Pop multiple bubbles in one shot<br>
🧠 Strategic Levels – Plan your moves carefully<br>
🪄 Power-Ups – Use special boosts to clear tough areas<br>
📈 Level Progression – Increasing difficulty with each stage<br><br>

<strong>🧠 Gameplay Mechanics</strong><br><br>

Aim precisely to create effective matches<br>
Use walls to bounce shots and reach tricky spots<br>
Clear floating bubbles for bonus points<br>
Manage your moves wisely to complete levels<br><br>

<strong>💡 Tips & Tricks</strong><br><br>

Aim for clusters to maximize pops<br>
Use bounce shots for hard-to-reach areas<br>
