Plan your moves ahead to avoid running out of shots<br><br>

<strong>🏁 Game Progression</strong><br><br>

Complete levels by clearing all bubbles. Earn stars based on your performance and unlock new challenges as you advance.<br>

Each level introduces new layouts and obstacles to keep the gameplay fresh.<br><br>

