<h2>Instructions</h2>
<p>
<strong>🎮 How to Play</strong><br><br>

Shoot bubbles toward groups of the same color to make them pop. Match three or more bubbles to clear them from the board.<br>

Your goal is to remove all bubbles using limited shots while achieving the highest score possible.<br><br>

<strong>🎯 Controls</strong><br><br>

Desktop:<br><br>

Move Mouse – Aim<br>
Left Click – Shoot bubble<br><br>

Mobile:<br><br>

Swipe – Adjust aim<br>
Tap – Shoot<br>
